metadata.author: R.L. Stine
metadata.description: In this R. L. Stine family-friendly scare fest, Amy and her friend, Lissa, dont know what to do about Arnies bullying, bad-boy behavior, and mean jokes and pranks. The little monster is ruining their lives!  The girls decide its payback time. Total humiliation for Arnie. They find a recipe for blue slime on a YouTube channel and mix a big bucket to pour over Arnie at his birthday party, but will their plans for revenge go too far?
